name: HKAppleWalkingSteadinessClassification
desc: A classification of a score based on the steadiness of the user’s gait.

items.name: init(for: HKQuantity)
items.desc: Creates a new classification for the provided percentage.

items.name: case ok
items.desc: A classification indicating that the stability of the user’s gait is within the normal range.

items.name: case low
items.desc: A classification indicating that the stability of the user’s gate is below normal.

items.name: case veryLow
items.desc: A classification indicating that the stability of the user’s gate is considerably below normal.

items.name: typealias HKAppleWalkingSteadinessClassification.AllCases
items.desc: A type representing an array of classifications.

items.name: static var allCases: [HKAppleWalkingSteadinessClassification]
items.desc: An array that contains all valid walking steadiness classifications.

items.name: var maximum: HKQuantity
items.desc: The minimum walking steadiness percentage for the classification.

items.name: var minimum: HKQuantity
items.desc: The maximum walking steadiness percentage for the classification.
